@startuml
!theme plain
actor User
participant Frontend
participant "LeaveManagement.API" as API
participant "LeaveRequestService" as SVC
participant "LeaveBalanceService" as BAL
database MySQL
collections Redis

User -> Frontend: Apply Leave
Frontend -> API: POST /api/leaves
API -> SVC: ApplyAsync
SVC -> BAL: ValidateSufficientBalanceAsync
BAL -> MySQL: Read balance
SVC -> MySQL: Save leave request
SVC -> Redis: Invalidate keys
API --> Frontend: Success
@enduml
